posts.subject: A violent proposal
posts.body:
https://archive.fo/bg7fY

Have never used twitter - would piss on twitter. Recognize they are likely guilty of spreading LOTS of misinformation. That's what advocates and zealots do. Twitter is engaged in the sale of outrage.

Don't care. Nor should any here care. 

But these continuing censorship efforts by Newsguard, mothers against drunk driving, PC meetoo, or PC racebaiting DO deserve a response....

So when you find yourself in a place where the Karma cost is low....say 6 months ETA from your deathbed - do us a favor and kill them all. Just McVeigh them - but with that nice Isis suicide bomber touch to keep the public's legal expenses low. Leave a simple note indicating that you just did your part to stop censorship.

Think the rest of these clowns won't get the message?

Those justice vigilantes who go after advertisers to shame them into dropping newspapers for their ads? Those people are fair game too. Make it gruesome. 

All "special people" must be killed. It's time to take out the trash. Let a thousand McVeighs bloom.

Think that bitch at youtube heard me?
